{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":149534,"duration_api_ms":124008,"num_turns":20,"result":"Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**`internal/adapters/docker/build.go`:**\n- Added `baseImageDigestLabel` constant (`cloche.baseimage.digest`)\n- Added `parseBaseImage()` — scans Dockerfile for the final `FROM` directive, handles `AS stage`, `--platform` flags, comments, and case-insensitive `FROM`\n- Added `baseImageID()` — runs `docker inspect --format {{.Id}}` to get the local image ID\n- Added `isBaseImageStale()` — compares stored base image digest label against current local base image ID\n- Modified `EnsureImage()` — after Dockerfile hash matches, calls `isBaseImageStale()` to check if base image changed locally\n- Modified `buildImage()` — now inspects the base image before building and stores its ID as `cloche.baseimage.digest` label\n\n**`internal/adapters/docker/build_test.go`:**\n- Added `TestParseBaseImage` — 8 sub-tests covering simple FROM, multi-stage (last FROM wins), scratch, no FROM, comments, lowercase, and `--platform` flag\n- Added `TestIsBaseImageStale_NoLabel` — verifies graceful handling when label is missing\n- Added `TestEnsureImage_StoresBaseImageDigest` — integration test verifying the label is set after build\n\nKey design decisions:\n- No `docker pull` — only compares locally available images (per requirements)\n- Missing label (old builds) is treated as non-stale — avoids forced rebuilds on upgrade\n- `scratch` base image is skipped since it has no digest to compare\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"704edf9b-135c-4fad-bd79-666e382f4c38","total_cost_usd":0.50450875,"usage":{"input_tokens":22,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22837,"cache_read_input_tokens":380335,"output_tokens":6860,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":22837,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterati